
                         -=[ Penalize ]=-

Usage:  penalize <who> <small, medium, great>#<reason>


	This command will allow you to penalize a knight for
acting in an inappropriate manner. For more information
on penalties, please read info deeds.

Examples:
penalize player small#stole a corpse
penalize player great#They killed a non-criminal


Related Topics: deeds, penalize 


